It is a framework designed to make life easier.

For Using This framework Need To Registered

Services.AddFramework(configuration, typeof(DependencyInjection).Assembly);


MediatR, MessageBus, DDD



This registers:
----------------
    IDispatcher as transient
    IEventDispatcher as transient
   
    ICommandHandler<,> concrete implementations as transient
    IQueryHandler<,>  concrete implementations as transient
    IEventHandler<>  concrete implementations as transient
   

This also registers open generic implementations for:

    INotificationHandler<>
    IRequestExceptionHandler<,,>
    IRequestExceptionAction<,>

-------------- 
EntityBase. AggregateRoot, Repository, UnitOfWork, Exception, ValueObject,